---
title: Cheesy Garlic Beef, Pork & Chorizo Quesadillas with Creamy Pesto Dressing & Corn Salsa
description: Dinner tonight is easy breezy and very cheesy! A touch of Cheddar cheese sprinkled over saucy beef, pork and chorizo in a filling that will blow you away, is a must for these quesadillas. Drizzle over a fresh and creamy pesto dressing to finish with a smile.
